bio: Building high-performance coding assistants @double_ide (YC W23). Previously at @KittyHawkCorp, @Waymo, and other robotics groups. Waterloo 🇨🇦

exceptional_ability.evidence: Ownership of nav system at Kitty Hawk; engineering at Waymo/other robotics; co-founder YC W23 startup solving perf issues in AI coding; transitions hard problems from autonomy to AI infra.

summary: Wesley is a strong robotics engineer with Waymo/Kitty Hawk experience now leading a YC-backed AI coding infra startup, demonstrating deep systems knowledge and ownership. Ideal for AI engineering roles leveraging autonomy/ML infra expertise.
strengths: Proven track record in hard robotics/autonomy engineering
